ttp_template:

  Number of ONTs that can be added: {{ONTS | ORPHRASE}}, success: {{SUCCESS}}
  PortID :{{PORT_ID | re("\\d+")}}, ONTID :{{ONT_ID | ORPHRASE}}
</group>

textfsm_template:
Value ONTS (\d+)
Value SUCCESS (\d+)
Value PORT_ID (\d+)
Value ONT_ID (\d+)

Start
  ^\s*Number\s*of\s*ONTs\s*that\s*can\s*be\s*added:\s*${ONTS},\s*success:\s*${SUCCESS} -> OntDetails

OntDetails
  ^\s*PortID\s*:${PORT_ID},\s*ONTID\s*:${ONT_ID} -> Record
  ^\s*$$
  ^. -> Error
